    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing variable M differential. This example is mechanically pristine: the rod bearings have been proactively replaced, the VANOS has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability the E46 chassis is renowned for. Meticulously maintained with zero deferred maintenance, this is a turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
