    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition is absolute. The exterior features a flawless, mirror-finish paint job with no stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches; the glass is crystal clear, and the factory alloy wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, the carpets are pristine under original floor mats, and the dashboard is free of any sun fading or cracking. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, investment-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
      "price": 46500.0,
